---
import PageContainer from "../components/PageContainer.astro";
import PageHeader from "../components/PageHeader.astro";
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms — hmziq.rs" description="Terms for using hmziq.rs.">
  <PageContainer>
    <PageHeader
      title="Terms"
      description="A straightforward set of conditions for reading, referencing, and using the site."
      class="mb-8"
    />
    <article class="prose legal-doc max-w-3xl">
      <div class="not-prose mb-8 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
        <span class="rounded-full border border-base-300 bg-base-200 px-3 py-1 font-mono text-[0.72rem] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-base-content/62">
          Terms Of Use
        </span>
        <span class="font-mono text-[0.72rem] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-base-content/48">
          Effective March 31, 2026
        </span>
      </div>

      <p>
        hmziq.rs publishes writing, notes, and references for general informational purposes. The
        content is provided in good faith, but it may change over time and is offered without any
        warranty of completeness, accuracy, availability, or fitness for a particular purpose.
      </p>

      <h2>Permitted use</h2>
      <p>
        You may read the site, reference it, and share links to its pages. Reasonable quotation
        with proper attribution is generally acceptable. If a specific post or asset includes a
        separate license, that license controls its use.
      </p>

      <h2>Content ownership</h2>
      <p>
        Unless otherwise stated, original writing and site materials remain the property of the site
        owner. Reuse beyond normal quotation, citation, or linking should be done with permission.
      </p>

      <h2>External links</h2>
      <p>
        The site may link to third-party websites, tools, or references. Those resources are not
        controlled by hmziq.rs and are governed by their own terms, policies, and availability.
      </p>

      <h2>Advertising and sponsorships</h2>
      <p>
        The site may include static advertisements, sponsorship placements, or promotional mentions.
        Unless stated otherwise, those placements do not change the ownership of the site content or
        the reader&apos;s responsibility to evaluate products, services, or external offers
        independently.
      </p>

      <h2>Acceptable conduct</h2>
      <p>
        You agree not to misuse the site, attempt unauthorized access, interfere with its
        infrastructure, or use the site in a way that could disrupt service for others.
      </p>

      <h2>Liability</h2>
      <p>
        To the fullest extent permitted by applicable law, hmziq.rs is provided on an &quot;as is&quot;
        basis. The site owner is not liable for losses, interruptions, or decisions made in
        reliance on the content published here.
      </p>
    </article>
  </PageContainer>
</BaseLayout>
